	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You add the <em>acid</em> and <em>poison</em> schools of magic to your fire lord spell list. You gain two spells from these schools when you gain this feature, they don’t count toward the number of spells you know.</p><p>Once per Long Rest, when you use the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.0VKJHXDtUHxvSFv0]{Searing Fire} feature, instead of burning, you can choose a number of creatures up to your proficiency bonus which were affected by your spell. They make a Constitution Saving Throw (Spell save DC), or are [[/condition id=poisoned]] for 1 minute. They make a new saving throw at the end of each of their turns.</p>",
